      "para_id": "Q000890.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Bau , the kind woman , the child of An , the lady of Iri-kug , his lady , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu and the E-ĝidru , his temple of seven niches , built her temple in Iri-kug ."
    }
  ],
